_sText:
THis is my second map

It is a deathrun map with 20 traps

I came up with some new ideas too.

19 of those traps can be activated by the Terrorist
and the other one is a field that kills the CT's if there is more than one on it. 

The terrorist moves on a higher level with speed mod.

If the CT finishes the map he will have speed mod and can kill the T's with an AK.

This is Version 2  please download play and comment.

* i added light
*fixed glitches and skybox
*fixed that u cant glitch fan


I am working on the final version with props and nicer design... but until then this version is very playable
